		<title>【增髮食物】14種食物幫助營養吸收促進頭髮生長</title>
		<link>https://www.she.com/health/%e5%a2%9e%e9%ab%ae-%e9%a3%9f%e7%89%a9-%e9%a0%ad%e9%ab%ae%e7%87%9f%e9%a4%8a/</link>
