		<title>Somi私物引熱話！「瑜珈環神器」戴住就可以瘦小腿？</title>
		<link>https://www.she.com/health/somi%e7%a7%81%e7%89%a9%e5%bc%95%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1%e7%91%9c%e7%8f%88%e7%92%b0%e7%a5%9e%e5%99%a8%e6%88%b4%e4%bd%8f%e5%b0%b1%e5%8f%af%e4%bb%a5%e7%98%a6%e5%b0%8f%e8%85%bf/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 03 Sep 2021 09:28:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ailey wong]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[beauty]]></category>
